messages.speech: I'm making some lunch. We are very busy now because we have to study for exams so I'm making something very quick. It's just some meat with salad and potatoes that are even not peeled if you look at it. Actually, I don't have myself eating potatoes in so hot climate because it's very hard to digest but Krustoff likes it a lot so we make everything together and then we'll see who eats what. I kind of like this food, it's enough for a day.
